<div data-layoutid="layoutid">
        <!-- .logoAndMacroses -->
        <div style="
        width: 346px;
        height: 187px;
            ">

            <!-- .macrosesAllContainer -->
            <div style="
            width: 304px;
            height: 157px;
            margin-left: 19px;
            margin-top: 17px;
            ">
                <!-- .logoContainer -->
                <div style="float: left;
                width: 304px;
                height: 85px;
                border: 0px solid #000;">
                    <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                        <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td>
                                <div data-cellinner="innereditablearea1-cellinner" style="width: 304px; height: 85px;">
                                    <div data-innereditablearea="innereditablearea1">
                                        <div style="
                                        width: 196px;
                                        height: 85px;
                                        margin: auto;
                                        overflow: hidden;
                                        ">
                                            <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," alt="Logotype" width="196" height="85">
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>
                <!-- .macrosContainer1 -->
                <div style="
                float: left;
                width: 304px;
                height: 24px;
                margin-top: 7px;">
                    <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                        <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td>
                                <div data-cellinner="innereditablearea2-cellinner" style="width: 304px; height: 26px; ">
                                    <div data-innereditablearea="innereditablearea2">
                                        <div style="
                                        white-space: nowrap;
                                        overflow: hidden;
                                        text-overflow: ellipsis;
                                        width: 304px;
                                        height: 24px;
                                        font-size: 20px;
                                        text-align: center;
                                        font-family: 'Arial';
                                        font-weight: bold;
                                        line-height: 1.1;"
                                            >
                                            {Contact_First_Name}{Contact_Last_Name}
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>
                <!-- .macrosContainer2 -->
                <div style="
                float: left;
                width: 304px;
                height: 16px;
                margin-top: 5px;
                margin-bottom: 3px;">
                    <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                        <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td>
                                <div data-cellinner="innereditablearea3-cellinner" style="width: 304px; height: 14px;">
                                    <div data-innereditablearea="innereditablearea3">
                                        <div style="
                                          white-space: nowrap;
                                          overflow: hidden;
                                          text-overflow: ellipsis;
                                          width: 304px;
                                          height: 14px;
                                          font-size: 12px;
                                          text-align: center;
                                          line-height: 1.1;
                                          font-family: 'Arial'
                                          ">
                                          Member ID: {User_ID}
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>
                <!-- .macrosContainer3 -->
                <div style="
                float: left;
                width: 304px;
                height: 14px;">
                    <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                        <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td>
                                <div data-cellinner="innereditablearea4-cellinner" style="width: 304px; height: 14px;">
                                    <div data-innereditablearea="innereditablearea4">
                                        <div style="
                                        white-space: nowrap;
                                        overflow: hidden;
                                        text-overflow: ellipsis;
                                        width: 304px;
                                        height: 14px;
                                        font-size: 12px;
                                        text-align: center;
                                        line-height: 1.1;
                                        font-family: 'Arial';"
                                            >
                                            Valid until {Member_Subsequent_Renewal_Date}
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>


            </div>

        </div>
</div>
